Run: mkdir tft to create TF
Run: cd tft
Run: touch provider.tf resource.tf to create the file
Run vi provider.tf resource.tf to edit the file
Run: terraform init to initialize TF 
Run: terraform plan to see what you have inside (to plan)
Run: terraform apply it will deploy EC2 instance (to apply)
Run: to change the instance go to your resource edit the file, save it then apply.
Run: terraform destroy: to destroy the infrastructure.

Terraform apply  -auto-approve
Terraform destroy -auto-approve

Terraform: IAAC 
AWS Provider
IAAC - Infrastructure as a Code

https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/aws/latest/docs
https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/aws/latest/docs/resources/instance

